The Bugatti Chiron Baguette is renowned for its distinctive design elements, including a dynamic, multi-layered dial that echoes the aerodynamic lines of the Bugatti Chiron. The vibrant orange and deep black sapphires create a visually stunning contrast, while the watch’s detailed craftsmanship ensures that each gem is perfectly aligned and securely set.

